{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Squingle is a cosmic 3D puzzle game that could only exist in VR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your challenge is to guide 2 spinning orbs to the goal through intricate, glass-like mazes called \u2018squingles.\u2019\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each level offers a mesmerizing visual experience, featuring dynamic, morphing sculptures that come to life in fully immersive environments or in Mixed Reality.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With intuitive controls and hand-tracking support, Squingle will captivate your mind and spirit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2728 100 LEVELS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Launching with 100 levels which will\u00a0 grow in complexity, featuring tighter spaces and new challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf08 A VISUAL MASTERPIECE</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each maze is a stunning, morphing sculpture, offering an unmatched visual experience in Mixed Reality or Fully immersive modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\udde9 EASY TO PICK, HARD TO MASTER</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Designed to be accessible for both newcomers to VR and experts seeking a transcendent experience, with intuitive controls and hand tracking support for seamless play, whether standing or seated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\ude0c RELAX &amp; UNWIND</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play on the sofa or in room-sized mazes. Squingle\u2019s calming gameplay will soothe your soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfc5 AWARDS</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Best VR Game ~ GDWC Finalist</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Finalist ~ QLDXR Festival</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cBest of the Quest\u201d ~ Gibby\u2019s Guide</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">FEATURES</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge Mode: Time trials and global leaderboards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Room/Mini scale: Play big or small!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Race your ghost: Beat your best times.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Into the Squingle!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1439040/4212a868fce30de67051854382168c526a3e120e.jpg"},{"name":"Big Bang","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1439040/eb2de770303f28e887681236856f51e8b3dd1181.jpg"},{"name":"Supermassive Black Hole","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1439040/39d3ace09e29a5fe9e8b6f8501c3db4bff6a4a18.jpg"},{"name":"Trillions of Stars","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1439040/51807167c1afa3bdbd730e866992f5b93ec23039.jpg"},{"name":"Trillions of Galaxies","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1439040/ccedfd5122f0399629fdd59fad98bf0accdc93c8.jpg"},{"name":"Neutrinos","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1439040/1d61ed1e7f7af380dd1ca5c8075cc94d7961dc04.jpg"},{"name":"The Higgs Boson","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1439040/bae1998f5cc91e1462ec4d81d6920b5b513432a1.jpg"},{"name":"Primordial Earth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1439040/71a3e3289cb3b35aa9a0f6cf79593de41a116f04.jpg"},{"name":"Abiogenesis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1439040/c1344915a1fb86393054d91396f49bd3f2ed10db.jpg"},{"name":"Reptilian Brain","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1439040/0eeec79f52f1dd058b2bb4c9223be0476b6c665f.jpg"}],"total":40},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st