 visual experience in Mixed Reality or Fully immersive modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\udde9 EASY TO PICK, HARD TO MASTER</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Designed to be accessible for both newcomers to VR and experts seeking a transcendent experience, with intuitive controls and hand tracking support for seamless play, whether standing or seated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\ude0c RELAX &amp; UNWIND</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play on the sofa or in room-sized mazes. Squingle\u2019s calming gameplay will soothe your soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfc5 AWARDS</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Best VR Game ~ GDWC Finalist</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Finalist ~ QLDXR Festival</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cBest of the Quest\u201d ~ Gibby\u2019s Guide</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">FEATURES</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge Mode: Time trials and global leaderboards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Room/Mini scale: Play big or small!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Race your ghost: Beat your best times.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Ben Outram"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1439040/header.jpg?t=1737470647","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257090729,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090729/movie480.mp4?t=1737470646","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090729/movie_max.mp4?t=1737470646"},"name":"January 2025","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257090729/a2b486a06580f3cf7b758cd3b1d43fd7997edbdb/movie_600x337.jpg?t=17